text: George Houvardas (born 1982) is an Australian actor. He is best known for his role as Nick "Carbo" Karandonis on the Seven Network television program Packed to the Rafters. Houvardas was born in Sydney, New South Wales and is of Greek origin. He began a career in television acting in 2008.
